      • buildNodeForType

        public static RefexDataTypeNodeDetails buildNodeForType(org.ihtsdo.otf.tcc.api.refexDynamic.data.RefexDynamicDataType dt,
                                                        org.ihtsdo.otf.tcc.api.refexDynamic.data.RefexDynamicDataBI defaultValue,
                                                        org.ihtsdo.otf.tcc.api.refexDynamic.data.RefexDynamicDataBI currentValue,
                                                        javafx.beans.property.SimpleStringProperty valueIsRequired,
                                                        javafx.beans.property.SimpleStringProperty defaultValueTooltip,
                                                        javafx.beans.property.ReadOnlyObjectProperty<org.ihtsdo.otf.tcc.api.refexDynamic.data.RefexDynamicDataType> polymorphicSelection,
                                                        UpdateableBooleanBinding allValid,
                                                        javafx.beans.property.ObjectProperty<org.ihtsdo.otf.tcc.api.refexDynamic.data.RefexDynamicValidatorType> validatorType,
                                                        javafx.beans.property.ObjectProperty<org.ihtsdo.otf.tcc.api.refexDynamic.data.RefexDynamicDataBI> validatorData)
        Parameters:
        dt - - The datatype of the node to be built
        defaultValue - - The default value for the node (null allowed)
        currentValue - - The current value for the node to prepopulate GUI (null allowed)
        valueIsRequired - - If this value must be set, pass in a SimpleStringProperty - it will be updated with a suitable message when the node is blank. If this value is not required, pass null.
        defaultValueTooltip - - If this field has a default value - as a convenience, this pass in a SimpleStringProperty here, and it will update the value as appropriate with a user friendly string explaining the default value. (null allowed)
        polymorphicSelection - - If the specified datatype of this node is polymorphic - the user has to choose a type for this instance. This is for the users choice. Null allowed, if the datatype is not polymorphic.
        allValid - - Bindings will be added to this UpdateableBooleanBinding depending on the node construction. The objects that were bound will be returned in the result object.
        validatorType - - if not null, data entered into the field will be validated against the validator.
        validatorData - - if not null (and validatorType is not null) data entered into the field will be validated against the validator.
